<subSubSection id="B967652DB0200ABF2D534B27042ED663" pageId="null" pageNumber="350" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="E9865EEAC5F2DB9CA62FE949F99E79FB" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Samtige Witwenblume</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="82FB1F3C8DA039CA7AD75939CC7B72F6" lastPageNumber="349" pageId="null" pageNumber="350" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCBF819C69A6962AF0014EBC04C7D28" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="DDD5AD475488D291B0AC910F379642C9" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caprifoliaceae" genus="Knautia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Dipsacales" pageId="null" pageNumber="350" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="transalpina">
<emphasis id="9539FBC399A57804146B70A6729B4DA8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">K. transalpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 5) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="3E5B3FE62ACE2C0FA4A58AC8618E6732" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
<normalizedToken id="9417CED1171234C1B51EFB2A659CA8A0" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
ober- und unterseits sehr dicht und abstehend behaart
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="4A2B019AB9B2236ECB6244182D5794D5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Haare 0,4</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="32E7633A32D3004573C2DEF4126775D2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">0,8 mm lang</emphasis>
), 
<emphasis id="0AA0EC4D30598EF289FC76797F9ADFB7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
<normalizedToken id="5687BA0FA59C5D8053DF6C37EFACABBA" originalValue="weißlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">weisslich</normalizedToken>
und samtig.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="0FCF38316E0682E68B5F391A0658F599" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="474947709BBB6EF3DCFAAEF61EA1A661" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
<emphasis id="88F2850860DDF1916E671F5B6A58DF93" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
<pageBreakToken id="89F97966170FAB85B8E3F23668422A01" pageId="null" pageNumber="349" start="start">Zytologische</pageBreakToken>
Angaben. 2n
</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="97511EC8E6446F2D61A344FB0779A3F5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">20:</emphasis>
Material vom Monte Tombea in Judikarien (Ehrendorfer 1962).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4DD9E297F10BB3DFC233C16147E18A67" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
<emphasis id="6095FEAFB9CE22E681D1F8EA88C7616C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan, seltener subalpin. Trockene, steinige, kalkhaltige 
<normalizedToken id="9498C9EDA9CE7149F80738C2000DB016" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="A59569AE3FC02DD31013F7B2056FBC6A" originalValue="wärmeren" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">waermeren</normalizedToken>
Lagen. Felsen, steinige 
<normalizedToken id="793320137157E7080BE7B628F6CEF435" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Haenge</normalizedToken>
, Trockenwiesen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E2974D40382C10FFD4CC66967B84B7D3" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
<emphasis id="3ACF1BDF17C05F4A7EE73AB1D6340C3E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="3DFFBBA4A797DB6F44400046C59851EE" originalValue="Südalpen-Pflanze" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Suedalpen-Pflanze</normalizedToken>
:
</emphasis>
Vom Luganersee 
<normalizedToken id="F087FE9CD198DC8B82F90EB42E3A7E6C" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Venetien. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="CA7B287A823F292D39DB244168277E96" originalValue="Südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">Suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin (z. B. Castagnola), 
<normalizedToken id="0B2CC13BFD4BF882157078D494FB57F7" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Comerseegebiet (z. B. Brianza), 
<normalizedToken id="E19A46C4E6EA3C585F35B9D5D3DB57B9" originalValue="südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="349">suedliche</normalizedToken>
Bergamasker Alpen (z.B. Val Sassina, Monte Albenga, San Bernardo bei Bergamo, Sedrina im Val Brembana, Presolana, Gebiet des Iseosees).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
